OL,3,CAlmost one hundred people now looking
OL,4,Cto move to Alderney each year
OL,6,FAlmost 100 people are now looking to
OL,7,Frelocate to Alderney each year,
OL,8,Faccording to one of the island's
OL,9,Fleading estate agents.
OL,11,FIslanders are pointing to political
OL,12,Finstability in the UK, low house
OL,13,Fprices, and a lack of residency
OL,14,Frequirements as reasons behind a
OL,15,Frecent spike in interest from people
OL,16,Flooking to move to the island.
OL,18,FAndrew Eggleston, Managing Director of
OL,19,FBell & Co, told ITV News his team is
OL,20,Fcurrently selling an average of 1.5 to
OL,21,Ftwo houses each week.
