OL,3,CAlmost one hundred people now looking
OL,4,Cto move to Alderney each year
OL,6,F"We can blame, or thank, the Labour
OL,7,FGovernment in the UK for that," Andrew
OL,8,Fexplained.
OL,10,F"There are people who've been thinking
OL,11,Fabout moving, and because of what's
OL,12,Fhappening politically and such over in
OL,13,Fthe UK, they've now decided, 'Okay,
OL,14,Fit's time to move'."
OL,16,FMr Eggelston also believes Alderney is
OL,17,Funiquely positioned as an attractive
OL,18,Fdestination for people hoping to
OL,19,Fescape the UK mainland.
