OL,3,CAlmost one hundred people now looking
OL,4,Cto move to Alderney each year
OL,6,F"They probably want to stay quite
OL,7,Fclose to the UK, and keep English
OL,8,Fspeaking - so it's the Channel Islands
OL,9,For the Isle of Man, with these all
OL,10,Fbeing low tax jurisdictions too."
OL,12,FHowever, with a three-bed home in
OL,13,FAlderney currently selling for an
OL,14,Faverage of #350,000-#400,000, house
OL,15,Fprices significantly undercut Guernsey
OL,16,Fand Jersey's markets.
OL,18,FThere are also no residency or housing
OL,19,Frequirements, equivalent to Guernsey's
OL,20,Fopen and local housing market or
OL,21,FJersey's tiered residency system.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/11
