OL,3,CAlmost one hundred people now looking
OL,4,Cto move to Alderney each year
OL,6,FIt means it is far easier for people
OL,7,Fto relocate to Alderney, as long as
OL,8,Fthey subsequently obtain a work permit
OL,9,Ffrom the island's States.
OL,11,FAndrew adds his team has witnessed an
OL,12,Finflux of people moving from Guernsey
OL,13,Fsince the pandemic - drawn in by the
OL,14,Fsimilar lifestyle and lower house
OL,15,Fprices.
OL,17,F"We have all of the benefits, but no
OL,18,Frestrictions", he explains, "so out of
OL,19,Fthe Channel Islands, Alderney wins."
