OL,3,CAlmost one hundred people now looking
OL,4,Cto move to Alderney each year
OL,6,FTreina Hartell, who moved her family
OL,7,Fof five to Alderney from Scotland last
OL,8,Fyear, says these were obvious draws -
OL,9,Falongside the pull of an island
OL,10,Flifestyle.
OL,12,F"Alderney ticked all of the boxes, and
OL,13,Fwhen we visited, we just fell in love
OL,14,Fwith it", Treina said, adding that the
OL,15,Fease of relocating was a bonus.
OL,17,F"Buying here - once we'd found the
OL,18,Fhouse that we fell in love with - was
OL,19,Fmuch simpler than buying and selling
OL,20,Fin the UK was."
