OL,3,CAlmost one hundred people now looking
OL,4,Cto move to Alderney each year
OL,6,FTreina was surprised to be dealing
OL,7,Fwith just an estate agent and the
OL,8,Fsellers, because conveyancing and a
OL,9,Flot of the legal work are
OL,10,Fpredominantly done in-house in
OL,11,FAlderney.
OL,13,F"It just felt smooth, and things just
OL,14,Fhappened the way things were meant to
OL,15,Fhappen."
OL,17,FIslanders are also optimistic there
OL,18,Fmight be a draw for people to move
OL,19,Fbusiness to the island, too.
