OL,3,CAlmost one hundred people now looking
OL,4,Cto move to Alderney each year
OL,6,FIan Corder, who set up Alderney's
OL,7,Ffirst Enterprise and Digital
OL,8,FTechnology hub in November, says he
OL,9,Fhas already garnered attention from
OL,10,Fpeople interested in setting up
OL,11,Fbusinesses on the island.
OL,13,F"From a business perspective, it's
OL,14,Freally easy for people to move here
OL,15,Fand work here as a UK citizen," he
OL,16,Fexplained.
