OL,3,CAlmost one hundred people now looking
OL,4,Cto move to Alderney each year
OL,6,FIan added that with a rise in digital
OL,7,Fbusinesses, people are still able to
OL,8,F"feel they're part of a global
OL,9,Fcommunity at the same time", with
OL,10,Finterest coming from a range of
OL,11,Fsectors - including finance, digital
OL,12,Fmarketing, and cyber security.
OL,14,F"I think it's really exciting what we
OL,15,Fcould be doing over the next couple of
OL,16,Fyears."
OL,18,FDespite a steady population rise over
OL,19,Fthe past couple of years, there
OL,20,Fremains concern that young islanders
OL,21,Fcontinue to leave.
