OL,3,CAlmost one hundred people now looking
OL,4,Cto move to Alderney each year
OL,6,FOne driver off the island could be the
OL,7,Flack of housing available to first-
OL,8,Ftime buyers.
OL,10,FWith the lack of residential
OL,11,Frequirements, anyone can, in theory,
OL,12,Fsee a house, buy it, and do what
OL,13,Fthey'd like with it.
OL,15,FThis has enabled a growing percentage
OL,16,Fof the private rental sector to be
OL,17,Fdominated by overseas landlords who
OL,18,Fuse the properties as second homes.
