OL,3,CAlmost one hundred people now looking
OL,4,Cto move to Alderney each year
OL,6,FThere is also no legislation currently
OL,7,Fin place allowing for banks to lend
OL,8,Ffor the purchase of leasehold
OL,9,Fproperties, which many cheaper
OL,10,Fproperties, such as apartments,
OL,11,Fcurrently are.
OL,13,FIt is something the island's Chamber
OL,14,Fof Commerce is working alongside the
OL,15,FStates of Guernsey to change.
OL,17,F"As soon as we get that through,
OL,18,Fyounger people can buy here for around
OL,19,F#150,000, which is great", Andrew
OL,20,Fexplained.
